@@yHot wind drives stinging sand across a vast expanse of rolling dunes. The sky above is a merciless white glare, and the horizon shimmers with heat haze in every direction. Faint tracks in the sand suggest that creatures pass through here, though the shifting dunes quickly erase all evidence.
  The dunes rise and fall like frozen waves, their crests trailing ribbons of sand into the scalding air. Somewhere in the distance, a low moan echoes across the wasteland as the wind funnels through unseen rock formations. The heat is suffocating, pressing down like a physical weight.@@N
