#29901
@@yShifting Sand Expanse@@N~
@@yThe sand here is fine and loose, swallowing each footstep ankle-deep. Desiccated scrub brush clings to the slopes of the dunes, rattling in the constant wind. A crumbling stone obelisk is visible to the east, while the terrain drops into sun-baked flats to the south.
  Heat mirages ripple across the sand, conjuring phantom lakes and ghostly towers on the horizon. The dunes stretch endlessly in every direction, their shifting surfaces erasing all sense of direction. A faint sulfurous smell rises from sun-baked mineral deposits beneath the sand.@@N
