@@yOasis of Shimmering Sands@@N~
@@yA small oasis pools in a rocky basin, fed by a trickle of water seeping from cracked stone. A few stubborn palms provide dappled shade, and the air here carries a faint coolness. Animal tracks of every description crowd the muddy banks of the shallow water.
  The water is clear but shallow, reflecting the palm fronds above in a shimmering mirror. Dragonflies hover over the surface, and the gentle plop of small frogs punctuates the relative quiet. This precious water source draws every living thing for miles, making it both a sanctuary and a hunting ground.@@N
