@@bOffering Chamber@@N~
@@bStone altars stand at the cardinal points of this circular chamber, their surfaces stained dark by centuries of ritual offerings. Clay vessels and ceremonial blades litter the dusty floor, and the faint scent of ancient incense still lingers in the stale air.
