@@bTrapped Hallway@@N~
@@bThis corridor's stone tiles are slightly uneven, some depressed more than others. Small holes dot the walls at regular intervals, their dark interiors hinting at hidden mechanisms. The bones of less cautious explorers lie scattered near several of the more obvious pressure plates.
