@@bSacred Pool@@N~
@@bA natural spring feeds a shallow pool of surprisingly clear water in a basin carved from the living rock. Offerings of coins and small statues lie beneath the surface, and the water glows with a faint phosphorescence from minerals dissolved in its depths.
