#29945
@@bCursed Vault@@N~
@@bWarning glyphs are carved into every surface of this sealed chamber, their paint still vivid after centuries. The air is unnaturally cold, and a persistent sense of dread permeates the space. Shattered remains of protective wards litter the threshold.
  The glyphs pulse with a sickly green luminescence, their magic still potent despite the ages. Frost crystals have formed on the stone surfaces despite the desert above, and each exhaled breath hangs as a visible cloud. The broken ward stones at the entrance crackle with residual energy, their failure having unleashed whatever was sealed within.@@N
