#29948
@@RLich's Sanctum@@N~
@@RA vast circular chamber lies at the heart of the deepest catacombs, illuminated by floating orbs of purple flame. Runic circles are etched into the obsidian floor in concentric rings, and towering bookshelves line the curved walls, filled with ancient tomes of forbidden knowledge.
  The purple flames cast writhing shadows that move independently of any physical source, dancing across the curved walls in hypnotic patterns. The bookshelves stretch from floor to ceiling, their contents ranging from crumbling papyrus scrolls to leather-bound grimoires that seem to breathe. The concentric runic circles pulse with alternating light, creating a mesmerizing and deeply disturbing rhythm.@@N
