#29951
@@bNarrow Tunnel@@N~
@@bThis cramped passage forces movement in single file, the rough stone walls pressing close on both sides. Sticky webbing clings to the ceiling, and the chittering of unseen creatures echoes from deeper within the cave system.
  The tunnel walls are scratched with parallel grooves from countless legs and tails scraping past over the years. Desiccated insect husks and shed exoskeleton fragments crunch underfoot, and the webbing overhead trembles with the vibrations of distant movement through the connected tunnel network.@@N
