#29964
@@yLookout Post@@N~
@@yA crude wooden platform has been erected atop a rocky outcrop, providing a commanding view of the surrounding desert. Tattered banners bearing a crossed-scimitar sigil snap in the wind, and discarded food scraps suggest a recent watch rotation.
  The platform creaks ominously in the wind, its construction crude but functional. A battered signal horn hangs from a peg, ready to sound the alarm. Empty water skins and gnawed bones scattered across the platform speak to the tedium of long watches under the merciless sun.@@N
