#29966
@@yRaider Camp Perimeter@@N~
@@yThe outer ring of the raider camp is a disorganized sprawl of lean-tos, cooking fires, and staked-out hides. The smell of unwashed bodies and roasting meat hangs heavy in the air. Armed figures move between the shelters with the casual menace of career brigands.
  Scavenged tarps and stolen canvas create a patchwork of shade over rough sleeping areas. Weapons are kept close at hand everywhere, and the camp has the restless energy of barely controlled violence. Dogs gnaw on bones between the tents, and the ever-present sand has worked its way into every surface.@@N
