#29967
@@ySupply Tent@@N~
@@yA large canvas tent serves as the warband's supply depot, its interior crammed with crates, barrels, and sacks of plundered goods. Stolen merchant wares are stacked haphazardly alongside weapons, armor, and provisions for the camp.
  Merchant guild stamps and trade house seals are still visible on many of the stolen crates, identifying their origins from caravan routes across the region. Spilled grain attracts rats and beetles in the darker corners, and the canvas walls billow gently in the desert breeze.@@N
