#29972
@@yWar Tent@@N~
@@yThis large reinforced tent serves as the command center of the raider warband. A sand table displaying a crude map of the surrounding territory dominates the interior, with carved wooden tokens marking targets and patrol routes across the region.
  The sand table is surprisingly detailed, showing trade routes, oasis locations, and the positions of rival warbands with carved tokens of different colors. Stolen maps and intercepted dispatches are pinned to the tent walls with daggers. A heavy ironbound chest serves as the warlord's field desk, its surface scarred with blade marks.@@N
