#29973
@@RWarlord's Pavilion@@N~
@@RA lavish pavilion of heavy canvas and stolen silk stands apart from the rest of the camp, its entrance flanked by lit braziers. Looted tapestries hang inside, and a throne cobbled together from broken furniture sits on a raised platform of packed earth.
  The pavilion is the largest structure in the camp, its canvas reinforced with layers of stolen silk and leather. Trophies from conquered rivals hang from the tent poles, including weapons, banners, and less savory mementos. The cobbled throne is a grotesque masterwork of broken chair legs, smashed table tops, and hammered-flat shield bosses, padded with stolen cushions.@@N
